        **Installation**
        
        pyrogen is installable directly from Pypi:
        ```
        pip install pyrogen
        ```
        
        
        
        **Documentation**
        
        Coming soon .... or not ^^
        <br>
        
        
        
        **Code Examples / Tutorials**
        
        If you want to run the very first demo scene, just use the following command :
        ```
        python -m pyrogen.tutorials.dev_test.dev_test
        ```
        
        
        
        
